sections.content:
The personal data collected is used for the following purposes:
- Creating user profiles;
- Providing a platform allowing users to access, share, and exchange data and datasets;
- Providing APIs for access to datasets;
- Monitoring the application of the present Terms of Use and of any legitimate and/or illegitimate use of the information, which also includes all measures to avoid fraud;
- Compiling statistics on attendance/downloads.
